37-1274.Amphibious vehicle; registration; certificate of title; provisions not applicable.

Sections 37-1211 to 37-1231 and 37-1275 to 37-12,108 shall not apply to an amphibious vehicle if a current and valid registration has been issued for such amphibious vehicle under the Motor Vehicle Registration Act.

SourceLaws 2025, LB97, ยง 5.Operative Date: April 15, 2025

Cross ReferencesMotor Vehicle Registration Act, see section 60-301.
